subclause.text:
absent the protection provided by the levee
				system, is subject to significant base flood elevations of not less than a
				reasonable height, as determined by the Administrator;

clause.text:
the footprint of
				the repaired and restored structure will not exceed the footprint of the
				original structure;

the number of
				floors of the repaired and restored structure will not exceed the number of
				floors of the original structure;

the elevation of
				the repaired and restored structure will be consistent with existing
				construction in the neighborhood;

no claims payments have been made under
				flood insurance coverage under this title for damages to or loss of the
				structure;
